This time the reason for the break-in on Wall Street.
In the Czech Republic, too, the reaction of the market to the result of the vote of the American House of Representatives, which it had refused to support a stabilisation plan for the local financial sector, is shown.
Stocks fall in Asia
A dramatic fall occurred on Tuesday, stocks on the stock exchanges in Asia, although indices were able to offset some of the losses over the course of the day.
The Hang Seng Stock Exchange index in Hong Kong lost almost four percentage points over the course of the business day, but was later able to offset some of the losses, thus decreasing to about 2.5 percent.
