Brussels had commissioned the independent scientific committee in view of the widespread use of portable music devices among young people.
"The scientists - the EU communication concludes - confirm that they are rightly concerned and that the European Commission, together with the other EU Members and those concerned, will now examine the necessary measures to better protect children and young people from the noise coming from portable music devices and similar devices ".
